<h1 class="title">About Me</h1>
<div class= "content">
<p>My name is Robby Brownlow. I have been working in outside sales for the last 7 years. During the <br>
  peak of the Bitcoin bull run in 2017, I started doing research on Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies.<br>
  Like most people, I was initially very skeptical. After watching the "Hidden Secrets of Money" series by <br>
  Mike Maloney on Youtube, I became fascinated with learning about the history of our monetary system.</p>

  <p>After countless hours of research, I came to the conclusion that Bitcoin and Digital Ledger Technology <br>
  were the way of the future! My goal now it to get a job working in the cryptocurrency ecosystem <br>
  and help usher the world into the new age of money!</p>
  <p>To see my LinkedIn page, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-brownlow-844aa9ab/" target="_blank">click here.</a></p>
